Help Type: topic
Topic: recipe

Recipes

Create an archive from Markdown:
  wikigraph create book.sdpub ./book.md
  cat article.md | wikigraph create article.sdpub --input-format markdown

Queue derived data:
  wikigraph queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task reading-graph --accept-cost
  wikigraph queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task reading-summary --accept-cost

Search and open objects:
  wikigraph search book.sdpub "恩典 婴儿洗礼"
  wikigraph get book.sdpub wikigraph://chunk/123
  wikigraph related book.sdpub wikigraph://chunk/123
  wikigraph evidence book.sdpub wikigraph://triple/Q162593/discusses/Q9476
  wikigraph pack book.sdpub wikigraph://entity/Q162593 --budget 5000

Export:
  wikigraph export book.sdpub --output-format markdown --output out.md

Transform without an archive:
  cat chapter.txt | wikigraph transform --input-format txt --output-format markdown
